dc_title_s: West Indies, South America, Chile, Golfo de Ancud--northern part (Raster Image)
dc_description_s: Prepared and published by the National Imagery and Mapping Agency. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. Relief shown by form lines, hachures, and spot heights.
